      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>KLEIN-Bertram. On December 27, 1999. Beloved husband of Bernice. Loving father of Robert (Hunnie) Klein, Judy (Steve) Grossman, Jill (Warren) Weinberg, Jack (Karen) Klein and Michael Klein. Dear brother of Sally Gilbert and adored grandfather of 10. Funeral services were held Thursday, December 30, at I. J. Morris, Hempstead, NY.</p>
